Name: Run Sensors
Text: If resolved - next turn +1 init +1 card

Name: Fakeout
Text: When this card resolves, look at the top two cards of your deck, choose one and apply that instead

Name: Combo Strike
Text: \footnotesize{When revealed, choose 2 of the top 3 cards of the deck and discard them - this card gains the sum of their movement, blocks and attacks}

Name: Parry High
Text: If consumed, deal 1H at melee range immediately

Text: If consumed, deal 1M at melee range immediately

Name: Parry Low
Text: If consumed, deal 1L at melee range immediately

Name: Feint High
Text: Deals no damage. If blocked, reveal the top card of your deck, do any attacks on that card, then put that card on the bottom.

Text: Deals no damage. If blocked, reveal the top card of your deck, do any attacks on that card, then put that card on the bottom.
